  "lyrics": "I said, I said, I said, shit... You hear me... That's all that shit I just wanted. Oh, I'm rumblin' on, I'm rumblin' on Letting go of my mistakes tonight It's in my past So I'm gonna keep walking on It's in my way From my mind and me moving on It's in my past Gotta close the book on the old me To make the new last Gotta let go of my past Treacherous path runs a dark vein Laughing at myself in the effort and vain Driving boiled thoughts against my brain Mistakes calling out my mental insane How many people I ever hurt? How many people I confused? Manipulated what I deserved and earned And I'm still here to learn It's in my past So I'm gonna keep walking on It's in my way From my mind and me moving on It's in my past Gotta close the book on the old me To make the new last Gotta let go of my past Do I get to have a normal stay? Or am I just too hurtful To surrender them for forgiveness? Trust me, you don't wanna know All I faced through sin It's in my past So I'm gonna keep walking on It's in my way From my mind and me moving on It's in my past Gotta close the book on the old me To make the new last Gotta let go of my past All I've lost in my unkindness All the selfishness that took love It goes today, it goes today No matter the pain it takes No matter the climb I deserve life And a brighter day It's in my past So I'm gonna keep walking on It's in my way From my mind and me moving on",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 3,
      "text": "I said, I said, I said, shit...",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 6,
      "text": "You hear me...",
      "start": 5.539999961853027
    },
    {
      "end": 12,
      "text": "That's all that shit I just wanted.",
      "start": 9.9399995803833
    },
    {
      "end": 19.459999084472656,
      "text": "Oh, I'm rumblin' on, I'm rumblin' on",
      "start": 14.180000305175781
    },
    {
      "end": 25.079999923706055,
      "text": "Letting go of my mistakes tonight",
      "start": 20.760000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 30.079999923706055,
      "text": "It's in my past",
      "start": 27.420000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 34.400001525878906,
      "text": "So I'm gonna keep walking on",
      "start": 31
    },
    {
      "end": 37.439998626708984,
      "text": "It's in my way",
      "start": 34.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 41.540000915527344,
      "text": "From my mind and me moving on",
      "start": 37.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 44.08000183105469,
      "text": "It's in my past",
      "start": 41.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 48.47999954223633,
      "text": "Gotta close the book on the old me",
      "start": 44.959999084472656
    },
    {
      "end": 50.79999923706055,
      "text": "To make the new last",
      "start": 48.47999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 54.599998474121094,
      "text": "Gotta let go of my past",
      "start": 50.79999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 58.2400016784668,
      "text": "Treacherous path runs a dark vein",
      "start": 55.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 62.040000915527344,
      "text": "Laughing at myself in the effort and vain",
      "start": 58.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 65.13999938964844,
      "text": "Driving boiled thoughts against my brain",
      "start": 62.040000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 69.04000091552734,
      "text": "Mistakes calling out my mental insane",
      "start": 65.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 72.4000015258789,
      "text": "How many people I ever hurt?",
      "start": 69.04000091552734
    },
    {
      "end": 74.80000305175781,
      "text": "How many people I confused?",
      "start": 72.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 78.76000213623047,
      "text": "Manipulated what I deserved and earned",
      "start": 75.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 81.86000061035156,
      "text": "And I'm still here to learn",
      "start": 78.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 85.69999694824219,
      "text": "It's in my past",
      "start": 82.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 89.4000015258789,
      "text": "So I'm gonna keep walking on",
      "start": 85.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 92.54000091552734,
      "text": "It's in my way",
